567
00:27:39,767 --> 00:27:41,200
They're not to blame, alright?

568
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:42,700
It's my fault.

569
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:45,433
I have a friend, an
 acquaintance actually,

570
00:27:45,433 --> 00:27:46,533
her name's Valerie.

571
00:27:46,533 --> 00:27:47,967
- Did you say Valerie?

572
00:27:47,967 --> 00:27:49,867
- Oh, I knew she was trouble
