576
00:27:55,067 --> 00:27:56,500
- We'll never do it again.

577
00:27:56,500 --> 00:27:58,933
- No, you're not my problem,
 but you might be my solution.

578
00:27:58,933 --> 00:28:00,967
You say KL Interactive
 has been developing

579
00:28:00,967 --> 00:28:02,167
a dangerous game?

580
00:28:02,167 --> 00:28:03,833
Well I believe
 that to be a fact.

581
00:28:03,833 --> 00:28:05,533
You think Valerie was kidnapped?

582
00:28:05,533 --> 00:28:06,800
So do I.

583
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,667
See, Valerie was working for me,

584
00:28:08,667 --> 00:28:11,933
she was, is one
 of my best agents,

585
00:28:11,933 --> 00:28:13,667
and I've lost contact with her.

586
00:28:13,667 --> 00:28:15,433
I need a team to rescue her.

587
00:28:15,433 --> 00:28:17,067
I need you.

588
00:28:17,067 --> 00:28:18,100
- Why us?

589
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:20,167
- Because KL Interactive
is closed down

590
00:28:20,167 --> 00:28:22,800
as tight as a drum, I
 can't get an agent inside.

591
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:25,367
They're so tied into the
 military industrial complex

592
00:28:25,367 --> 00:28:27,100
that they know who
 all my agents are.

593
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,600
- So you want us?

594
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:31,733
- Yes, because no one would
 believe I would use kids.

595
00:28:31,733 --> 00:28:33,333
I really have no choice.

596
00:28:33,333 --> 00:28:35,133
- We don't know
 anything about spying.

597
00:28:35,133 --> 00:28:36,400
We're just teenagers.

598
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:37,700
- Yeah, it's teenagers.

599
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,933
- In the next few days,
you'll become bigger,

600
00:28:39,933 --> 00:28:42,467
better and brawnier than
you've ever imagined,

601
00:28:42,467 --> 00:28:43,633
with training.

602
00:28:43,633 --> 00:28:45,733
- (sighs incredulously)
What about school?

603
00:28:45,733 --> 00:28:47,433
What about our parents?

604
00:28:47,433 --> 00:28:48,467
What about homework?

605
00:28:48,467 --> 00:28:50,167
- Now you leave that to me.

606
00:28:50,167 --> 00:28:51,333
I'll prepare a letter saying

607
00:28:51,333 --> 00:28:53,233
you'd been accepted
 into a special

608
00:28:53,233 --> 00:28:57,167
