611
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:04,067
(light music)
 Gotta love it.

612
00:29:04,067 --> 00:29:05,567
(military drumming music)
 - Come on, maggot,

613
00:29:05,567 --> 00:29:07,067
you can do it, come on!

614
00:29:07,067 --> 00:29:08,233
Two, one, two!

615
00:29:09,300 --> 00:29:10,633
- I did those numbers already,

616
00:29:10,633 --> 00:29:11,800
