 your opponent.

658
00:30:45,133 --> 00:30:47,833
(Andrew screams a battle cry)

659
00:30:47,833 --> 00:30:50,900
(hits thud on flesh)

660
00:30:57,767 --> 00:31:00,233
(gong rings loudly)

661
00:31:00,233 --> 00:31:01,400
(Rocky barks)

