00:32:33,900 --> 00:32:34,967
- [Voiceover] I got him!

692
00:32:34,967 --> 00:32:35,800
Hey!

693
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,067
- Hey!

694
00:32:44,667 --> 00:32:46,933
Come back here with my bag.

695
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,533
Get him.

696
00:32:51,600 --> 00:32:53,133
He dropped the bag.

