 to remain silent.

716
00:33:48,933 --> 00:33:50,500
- I knew they weren't ready.

717
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:53,067
(Rocky barks)

718
00:34:02,067 --> 00:34:04,167
- Well what do you think?

719
00:34:06,833 --> 00:34:09,267
- I think you need another
 six months of training,

720
00:34:09,267 --> 00:34:12,200
I think if this works,
it's gonna be a miracle.

721
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,433
- You mean we got no choice?

722
00:34:13,433 --> 00:34:14,267
- Exactly.

723
00:34:15,267 --> 00:34:16,333
We begin now.

