most powerful men in the world.

735
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:43,700
As you know, he's
 developing a weapon

736
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:46,467
disguised as a game, but
 that's all we know about him.

737
00:34:46,467 --> 00:34:49,100
Your mission is to sneak
into KL Interactive

738
00:34:49,100 --> 00:34:51,633
