00:34:55,667 --> 00:34:57,067
- Wait a minute!

742
00:34:57,067 --> 00:34:59,333
Valerie's email message,

743
00:34:59,333 --> 00:35:00,867
maybe there's a clue.

744
00:35:00,867 --> 00:35:03,967
(intense music)

745
00:35:03,967 --> 00:35:06,467
(loud typing)

746
00:35:08,767 --> 00:35:10,067
- Andrew, stop
 playing with the game,

747
00:35:10,067 --> 00:35:13,633
